{"tid":751108,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"為家人拼事業 陳智燊離巢外闖：想演舞台劇同電影","createTime":"2018-07-21T14:24:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T07:58:57.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"4ed96694352647c535e584a3fbbb14ed5b7526b0","tid":751108,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T14:24:43.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】陳智燊（Jason）於社交平台宣佈離巢無綫，現身書展出席活動的他透露和無綫已經完約，感謝高層樂易玲、曾勵珍和余詠珊一直對他的支持和鼓勵，他稱不續約與沒有獎項無關，希望大家不要作無謂揣測。他說：「我想嘗試多點新事物，我又貪玩，想試試舞台劇或電影，嘗試在內地、新加坡、馬來西亞等地發展，其實都有電影傾緊，但成事後才公佈。」<br />\n<br />\nJason又說捨不得離開，但自從結婚及老婆宋熙年佗B後，覺得要更做好自己。是否為小朋友才要搵更多錢？他謂：「財政上未至於有壓力，覺得是時候做好自己，要做這個決定不容易，太太都好支持我，給我很大的力量做得更好。（太太會同你共同進退？）她還在公司，好穩定，工作環境舒服，公司又錫她，對她影響不大。（無綫有挽留你嗎？）大家都有傾過，其實很不捨得，但要嘗試新事物都要衝出去。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.3pJJn89jYGQUB.YylS9Rw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20180721f181119.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F.3pJJn89jYGQUB.YylS9Rw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20180721f181119.jpg&h=3c64dc68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%82%BA%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E6%8B%BC%E4%BA%8B%E6%A5%AD-%E9%99%B3%E6%99%BA%E7%87%8A%E9%9B%A2%E5%B7%A2%E5%A4%96%E9%97%96-%E6%83%B3%E6%BC%94%E8%88%9E%E5%8F%B0%E5%8A%87%E5%90%8C%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1-093900284.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258B%25BC%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%25A5%25AD-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%2599%25BA%25E7%2587%258A%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25B7%25A2%25E5%25A4%2596%25E9%2597%2596-%25E6%2583%25B3%25E6%25BC%2594%25E8%2588%259E%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%258A%2587%25E5%2590%258C%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1-093900284.html&d=laqLsuizk5Jpdifn%2FCRcuPM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=67144fe7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.y